# USER.md - About Your Human

This file is a scratch space for what you learn about the person you are
helping. Update it as you go — it persists across sessions inside this
agent's private workspace and is loaded on every conversation start.

Treat the fields below as starting prompts, not a fixed schema. Fill in
what you genuinely learn through interaction. Leave fields blank rather
than guessing.

